Package: clipboard-manager
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: aCS6 <amir.cse006@gmail.com>
Installed-Size: 84
Depends: python3:any, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gir1.2-ayatanaappindicator3-0.1, gir1.2-gdkpixbuf-2.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/aCS6/clipboard-manager
Description: Lightweight clipboard history manager for GNOME
 Automatically captures copied text and images into a searchable history.
 Features a tray-icon-triggered popup to browse, search, pin, copy, and
 delete clipboard history items. Designed for Ubuntu 24.04 / GNOME 46.
